<section xml:id="xhprof.installation" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
 &reftitle.install;

 <para>
  To install XHProf, you are currently required to <link xlink:href="https://github.com/facebook/hhvm/wiki#building-hhvm">build HHVM from source</link> using the <literal>cmake -D HOTPROFILER:BOOL=ON</literal> when compiling. For example, when compiling HHVM, you would do something like this:
  <informalexample>
    <programlisting role="bash">
<![CDATA[
cd hhvm
git submodule update --init
cmake -D HOTPROFILER:BOOL=ON .
make
]]>
    </programlisting>
  </informalexample>
 </para>

</section>


